g.text: S. Maiti designed and ideated the overall research. S. Mishra ran the MC/MD codes and made structure related
graphics. Both S. Maiti and S. Mishra jointly wrote the manuscript and analysed the results. D.B. Sridhar
developed the code for MC/MD technique. B. Rai contributed to discussions and guidance of this work.
